{"TopicId":180125,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"A \u0026quot;KSP Loading...\u0026quot; Preview: New Idle Animations","CreatedByName":"SQUAD","CreatedById":66485,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-11-27T18:59:22Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T07:13:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223498456\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543874257\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002232383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dr.phees\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, dr.phees said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0would prefer you to make Kerbals...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- not drift on ladders (WHY NOT STICK THEM THERE - YOU DO NOT SLIDE ON LADDERS)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- not fall off even slightly moving vehicles\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- not slide on even the least inclined surface\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThat\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E would be \u003Cem\u003Einfinitely\u003C/em\u003E better than idle animations. I mean, how often do they really stand around in our view compared to falling off stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell sure, but that is not an artist/animator\u0027s problem, that\u0027s an entirely different problem all together \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T08:07:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022220px-Liegestuetz02_ani_fcm.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022148\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Liegestuetz02_ani_fcm.gif/220px-Liegestuetz02_ani_fcm.gif\u0022 width=\u0022220\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T09:13:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223498646\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543907634\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthat\u0027s an entirely different problem all together \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChorus: \u0022That\u0027s an entirely different problem!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T10:48:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223498674\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543914832\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChorus: \u0022That\u0027s an entirely different problem!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve found a problem where my Kerbal slides off the ladder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe set of rungs that allow them to climb up and down. But that\u0027s not important right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T11:10:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile we\u0027re talking about animations, has anyone noticed that Kerbals can turn their heads to the side on a ladder if you press Shift?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T13:23:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223498705\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543921826\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile we\u0027re talking about animations, has anyone noticed that Kerbals can turn their heads to the side on a ladder if you press Shift?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s not simply an animation, it has an actual function: press a directional key and the kerbal will attempt to jump and grab on to another nearby ladder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dr.phees","CreatedById":32383,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-04T13:30:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223498646\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543907634\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002262955\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Deddly\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Deddly said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell sure, but that is not an artist/animator\u0027s problem, that\u0027s an entirely different problem all together \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk. Rephrased:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurrently I would prefer SQUAD/4k to put developers on the job of improving KSP, not artists.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBetter?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe reason is, that there are so *many* little bugs, that exist forever and finally fixing them would actually polish the game play a lot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-12-04T13:32:25Z\u0022 title=\u002212/04/2018 01:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 4, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by dr.phees\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-05T00:08:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223498749\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221543930227\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002232383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dr.phees\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, dr.phees said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe reason is, that there are so *many* little bugs, that exist forever and finally fixing them would actually polish the game play a lot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn my experience, the bugs that stick around the longest are the hardest to fix. It\u0027s possible they just haven\u0027t figured it out yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd hiring more programmers does not fix bugs faster. Generally it makes it take longer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MR L A","CreatedById":150940,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-07T12:51:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese are some REALLY nice touches... KSP is slowly becoming a nicely polished game imo... if only I had a rig powerful enough to play it at a decent fps lol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WildBill","CreatedById":98829,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-07T19:36:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI disagree with the term \u0027Polished\u0027. Adding improved artwork is really great. Love it. But I cannot call this game \u0027polished\u0027 with the number of bugs and severe memory leakage I encounter at every turn. My latest example: launch an \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E to orbit. Takes a while, thanks to the stutter caused by poor garbage collection. Perfmon shows pretty steady memory leakage the whole time too. But I eventually make it and everything looks great. Now \u0027Switch to\u0027 another orbiting ship, and immediately \u0027Switch to\u0027 back. Both of my \u0027Medium Landing Gear\u0027 are now rotated all out of whack. Every \u0027Switch to\u0027 rotates them to a new random position. Makes landing impossible! I managed to manually edit the \u0027persistent.sfs\u0027 game file to fix the orientation, but I suspect only a handful of gamers would be able to do that. That should never be needed with a \u0027polished\u0027 game. My opinion of KSP is that it\u0027s at the far opposite end of the \u0027polished\u0027 spectrum right now...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T00:05:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother animation suggestion, when the animators have nothing better to do: Y. M. C. A!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T03:25:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223507137\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545177914\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother animation suggestion, when the animators have nothing better to do: Y. M. C. A!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe there are copyright issues involved there.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T11:10:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223507230\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545189928\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe there are copyright issues involved there.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmmm, true, given the problems Fortnite is having, but it\u2019s not an issue if they get permission first. And it\u2019s not like the animations are being sold one-by-one as microDLCs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T12:48:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe Viliage People should make a comeback dressed as Kerbals?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T13:26:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDevelopers - Should we add more animations that reflect gameplay and bring more life to the world?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlayers - Add wacky dances!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"V7 Aerospace","CreatedById":156062,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T17:20:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223507378\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545225981\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDevelopers - Should we add more animations that reflect gameplay and bring more life to the world?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlayers - Add wacky dances!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m all for wacky dances...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003Eas long as we can toggle them\u00A0\u003Cu\u003Eoff.\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vexillar","CreatedById":178802,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-12-19T18:24:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223507484\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221545240059\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156062\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022V7 Aerospace\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, V7 Aerospace said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nas long as we can toggle them\u00A0\u003Cu\u003Eoff.\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIndeed... not sure I\u0027d be keen on Kerbal Salsa Party 1.7...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}